omplex;</li><li>sustaining the relevance and effectiveness of DOEâ€™s nonproliferation efforts;</li><li>addressing the continued and related problems of DOEâ€™s contract administration and project management, especially for DOEâ€™s large and complex projects; and</li><li>addressing the departmentâ€™s human capital challenge of developing and retaining a skilled workforce capable of overseeing these projects.</li></ul></div>
      
